💪【Ultra Strong】The ideal utensil set you can pick up is the one that fits your cooking lifestyle. Our Kikcoin silicone utensils for cooking have the superior combination of materials—— food-grade soft silicone and a high-strength inner core of stainless steel and nylon. It helps to maintain an initial optimal memory state and enhance toughness.

🔥【Withstand High Temperature】Silicone is more inert than plastic. Our silicon utensils heat resistant sustain high temperatures to 446°F. These Kikcoin kitchen cooking utensils never melt slightly, even after you forget them on the cookware or next to the burner for a while. 🌴【Ergonomic Design】The shape and premium wood handle of the silicone kitchen utensils set in this set is ergonomic. It also provides protects against rust and scald. If you tackle all the recipes you can find and are always in the kitchen, you deserve this set.

✅【Easy to Store】 You'll also receive a kitchen utensil holder for convenient storage and always keep these nonstick utensils cooking set in dry condition and orderly. Kindly note that the wooden handle kitchen set is NOT dishwasher available.

❗【Warm Tips】Wooden handle product is not recommended to enter into dishwasher, please wash them by hands and don’t soak them in water for hours. Please dry them after washing and store in the utensil holder in daily use.
